amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"68\" data-width=\"286\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"608469370\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"b764f225-9112-4313-ba5a-1f74750b8767.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"608469325\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"2\" data-media-id=\"6d724d5c-260d-4a36-9677-0cd5490836e3\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/608469325/b764f225-9112-4313-ba5a-1f74750b8767.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758286260671&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=286&amp;height=68 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/608469325/b764f225-9112-4313-ba5a-1f74750b8767.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758286260671&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=200&amp;height=47 1x\" /></span></a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<hr /><h1 id=\"OfficialSwatch-Overview\">Overview</h1><p>It's the official RenderMan Shader Swatch!</p><p>This hip new version features improved topology, UVs, and more look development options than ever before, including glasses, cloth, liquids, fur, hair, and volumes...and with three lighting setups, it's easier than ever to get creative when building your materials.</p><p>The Official RenderMan Shader Swatch is available as a Maya or Blender project and in Alembic format to get started in your favorite Bridge Product.</p><p /></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout two-equal\" data-layout=\"two-equal\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<h3 id=\"OfficialSwatch-Main\"><strong><span data-colorid=\"j4fnyd4zfd\">Main</span></strong></h3><ul><li><p>Solid Teapot</p></li><li><p>22cm (<a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Human_head\" rel=\"nofollow\">average length of human head</a>)</p></li><li><p>Macbeth charts and spheres</p></li><li><p>Floor grid for refractive surfaces</p></li></ul></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p /></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout three-equal\" data-layout=\"three-equal\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"RenderMan_Swatch_Mirror.jpg\" width=\"221\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/608469325/RenderMan_Swatch_Mirror.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758286539020&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=221&amp;height=221\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/608469325/RenderMan_Swatch_Mirror.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758286539020&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"1024\" data-width=\"1024\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"608010621\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderMan_Swatch_Mirror.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"608469325\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"2\" data-media-id=\"9cd7bdad-393c-4584-817d-2b213ac86303\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/608469325/RenderMan_Swatch_Mirror.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758286539020&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=442&amp;height=442 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/608469325/RenderMan_Swatch_Mirror.jpg?version=1&